{"tid":1546233,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[買護陰] 譚凱邦稱其助理被捕後　遭警揸下體及涼茶潑面","createTime":"2019-09-06T08:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T19:06:57.000Z","uid":224066,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"45aa6037ebc9b45974a3e5c29bbfd95b0c89902f","tid":1546233,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190906/photo/bkn-20190906152236015-0906_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190906153928\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190906%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190906152236015-0906_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190906153928&h=e5f68a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反修例遊行示威下，港鐵多次封站，荃灣區議員譚凱邦今(6日)稱，其議員助理張先生(化名)在8月25日於港鐵葵芳站被警方以襲警為由拘捕，期間被粗暴對待，更被警員「揸下體」。<br />\n譚稱，港鐵疑似協助警察執法，封鎖葵芳站時將所有出入口的縫隙都加以阻擋，使該站變密閉空間，難以監察及採訪。從記者會上展示、張提供的片段到，<span style=\"color: red;\">他當日於站內被捕後，遭警員用胡椒噴劑噴向面部，又用涼茶潑向面部及「揸下體」，被警員毆打及用手指塞口</span>，其後他與警員乘港鐵到荃灣，在到達荃灣警署後才獲准去醫院。<br />\n譚指，張被拘留46小時後於醫院獲准保釋，現已拒絕保釋，譚正向港鐵索取當日站內閉路電視片段以便向投訴警察課投訴，並會與律師商討進一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs1.shop123.com.tw/200373/upload/standard/2003739425source_picture_439240.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs1.shop123.com.tw%2F200373%2Fupload%2Fstandard%2F2003739425source_picture_439240.jpg&h=385a5a62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3493a87fbd0e32f5d8321597634a4d0cf77f32b9","tid":1546233,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:07:29.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=fbf28481\" data-au